OL,3,C'They should've known': Reaction to
OL,4,CHull KR U-turn over P&O Ferries
OL,5,Csponsorship
OL,7,F"For the sake of a few quid I hope
OL,8,FRovers reconsider as this is the
OL,9,Fpoorest decision they have made in my
OL,10,Fopinion since the new board."
OL,12,FP&O Ferries sacked almost 800 workers
OL,13,Fwith immediate effect in March 2022 -
OL,14,Fincluding 82 seafarers on the Pride of
OL,15,FHull ferry from the city's port - in a
OL,16,Fmove which was heavily criticised by
OL,17,Funions and politicians on all sides.
OL,18,FThe staff were then largely replaced
OL,19,Fby agency workers who were paid lower
OL,20,Fwages.
