OL,3,C'They should've known': Reaction to
OL,4,CHull KR U-turn over P&O Ferries
OL,5,Csponsorship
OL,7,FThe company said the decision had been
OL,8,F"necessary" to ensure its survival.
OL,10,FThe firm's chief executive, Peter
OL,11,FHebblethwaite, appeared in front of
OL,12,FMPs on Tuesday, following an ITV News
OL,13,Fand The Guardian investigation which
OL,14,Frevealed the company was still paying
OL,15,Fsome of its workers less than #5 per
OL,16,Fhour.
OL,18,FDuring the session, he admitted that
OL,19,Fhe would not be able to live on the
OL,20,Fsame wage, with Mr Hebblethwaite was
OL,21,Faccused of being a "modern day pirate".
