OL,3,C'They should've known': Reaction to
OL,4,CHull KR U-turn over P&O Ferries
OL,5,Csponsorship
OL,7,FIn a statement on its website, Hull KR
OL,8,Fsaid it had entered into the
OL,9,Fpartnership "in good faith" and that
OL,10,Fit was aware of P&O Ferries' "desire
OL,11,Fto contribute to the city of Hull".
OL,13,FIt went on to say it had
OL,14,F"underestimated the continuing depth
OL,15,Fof feeling" following the controversy
OL,16,Fof two years ago.
