OL,3,C'They should've known': Reaction to
OL,4,CHull KR U-turn over P&O Ferries
OL,5,Csponsorship
OL,7,F"As an east Hull institution looking
OL,8,Fto stay true to its values, it's
OL,9,Fimportant to us that our community
OL,10,Fknow we will always try to do the
OL,11,Fright thing, and to represent them in
OL,12,Fthe best way possible," the statement
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,F"Therefore, Hull KR have decided at
OL,16,Fthis time it is inappropriate to
OL,17,Fcontinue with this partnership."
