OL,3,C'They should've known': Reaction to
OL,4,CHull KR U-turn over P&O Ferries
OL,5,Csponsorship
OL,7,FThe U-turn has been well-received by
OL,8,Ffans online praising it as the "right
OL,9,Fdecision", including Mr Moore, who
OL,10,Ffollowed up his previous post with
OL,11,Fanother crediting the club for
OL,12,Frecognising the "strength of feeling".
OL,14,F"It takes guts to change course in
OL,15,Fbusiness, so credit to all involved
OL,16,Fwho advised the club on this matter,"
OL,17,Fhe said.
